des: "This dip couldn't be easier!  We had friends drop in unexpectedly, so I created this using what I had on hand.  Everyone loved it! Make sure you've got some tortilla chips on hand."
ins: In a slow cooker, combine chili, cream cheese, and Cheddar cheese. Set the slow cooker to a low temperature, and let the dip cook until all of the cheeses have melted. Serve warm.
